Spinach Salad with Grilled Chicken and Balsamic Vinaigrette

25 min
$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-protein

Description

A fresh and vibrant spinach salad topped with juicy grilled chicken, drizzled with a tangy balsamic vinaigrette.

Ingredients

  • fresh spinach: 4 cups
  • grilled chicken breast: 1
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1
  • red onion: 1/4
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup
  • balsamic vinaigrette: 1/4 cup
